                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The viking guard has a charge, and that creature is adjacent to the viking guard</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Raising shields, the viking guard Strides up to twice its Speed as it protects its charge. The viking guard gains a +2 circumstance bonus to its AC against reactions triggered by this movement. The viking guard's charge can Stride the same distance as a reaction, moving with the troop to maintain the bonuses from Guard Charge during this movement.</p>"
